Create a new experience with the given parameters.

Parameters:
trustor - the trustor agent
trustee - the trustee agent
issue - the particular issue to which this experience relates
observation - the real, observed (objective) outcome of the interaction
evaluation - the evaluated (subjective) outcome of this interaction
peFunction - the performance evaluation function used to produce the evaluation
timeStep - the time step at which this experience was created
